[The attempt now in progress to determine how PPV entered Canada may yield
important information, but it is a formidable task to say the least. I
would not be surprised if a traveller from abroad brought unwittingly
brought PPV-infected budwood to Canada illegally. As I mentioned recently
in my comments on another posting on this disease, I saw a tourist at
Schiphol airport loading plant cuttings into plastic bags and stuffing them
into his pockets before departing for New York. - Mod.DH
